The F-Droid project endorses and supports two free software funding platforms:
  Liberapay
    Supports recurring donations, not linked to promise of recompense.
    Processed by Stripe or Paypal (creator needs their own account).
    Creator's identity is confirmed by an account on GitHub, Twitter,
      Mastodon, Google, GitLab, YouTube, Facebook, Twitch, OpenStreetMap,
      Bitbucket, LinuxFr.org, or Pleroma.
    Aug 2020: 5003 active users, 4313 giving money
  OpenCollective
    Focus on co-op communities with multiple members, and providing financial
    transparency to those members.
